---
title: Crypter 2
headerEmpty: true
footerHide: true
---
extends layouts/layout
block content
	// mint
	.mint
		.mint__col
			.mint__wrap
				form.mint__form
					.mint__head
						.mint__title.h1 Mint NFT
						a.button-circle.mint__back(href="index.html")
							+i('arrow-left')
					.mint__info Deploy a smart contract to showcase a series of NFT artworks.
					.field.field_icon.field_large
						.field__wrap
							input.field__input(type="text" name="title" value="The Explorer" placeholder="NFT title" required)
							+i('edit')
					.field.field_icon.field_large.field_textarea
						.field__wrap
							textarea.field__textarea(name="description" placeholder="Description" required) We are laying the groundwork for web3 â€” the next generation of the internet full of limitless possibilities. Join the millions of creators, collectors, and curators who are on this journey. Official website: crypter.net
							+i('edit')
					.mint__box
						.mint__category Collection
						.mint__collection
							.mint__preview
								img(src="img/content/balls.jpg" alt="")
							.mint__details
								.mint__subtitle Escape
								.mint__price 12 NFTs
							.mint__check
								+i('check')
					.mint__btns
						a.button-stroke-grey.button-large.mint__button(href="mint-nft-preview-mode.html") Preview
						a.button-large.mint__button(href="mint-nft-congrats.html")
							span Mint
							+i('arrow-right')
		.mint__col
			// upload
			.upload
				.upload__stage.h3 Upload your NFT
				.upload__file
					img(src="img/content/main-pic-1.jpg" alt="")
				.upload__title.h3 The Explorer
				.upload__item
					.upload__preview
						img(src="img/content/cute-planet-1.png" alt="")
					.upload__wrap
						.upload__subtitle Cute Planet
						.upload__price 12 NFTs
					.upload__lines

			